first run this cmd for package
npm init -y

then run this cmd to install express mongoose dotenv
npm install express mongoose dotenv

for auto refresh run this cmd
npm i nodemon -D

in frontend folder enter this cmd
npm create vite@latest .

after that run 
npm i

then install chakra ui run this cmd

npm i @chakra-ui/react@2 @emotion/react @emotion/styled framer-motion

after we can add router react run this cmd
npm i react-router-dom

react icon cmd
npm i react-icon


to access in any where run this cmd
npm i zustand